{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.1","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:1","prev_osis_id":"Lev.004.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. L\u00e9 4:22-35. Pr 28:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsque quelqu\u2019un, apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 mis sous serment comme t\u00e9moin, p\u00e9chera en ne d\u00e9clarant pas ce qu\u2019il a vu ou ce qu\u2019il sait, il restera charg\u00e9 de sa faute.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.35","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.2","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:2","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Lorsque quelqu\u2019un, sans s\u2019en apercevoir, touchera une chose souill\u00e9e, comme le cadavre d\u2019un animal impur, que ce soit d\u2019une b\u00eate sauvage ou domestique, ou bien d\u2019un reptile, il deviendra lui-m\u00eame impur et il se rendra coupable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.3","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:3","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Lorsque, sans y prendre garde, il touchera une souillure humaine quelconque, et qu\u2019il s\u2019en aper\u00e7oive plus tard, il en sera coupable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.4","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:4","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Lorsque quelqu\u2019un, parlant \u00e0 la l\u00e9g\u00e8re, jure de faire du mal ou du bien, et que, ne l\u2019ayant pas remarqu\u00e9 d\u2019abord, il s\u2019en aper\u00e7oive plus tard, il en sera coupable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.5","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:5","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Celui donc qui se rendra coupable de l\u2019une de ces choses, fera l\u2019aveu de son p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.6","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:6","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Puis il offrira en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, pour le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis, une femelle de menu b\u00e9tail, une brebis ou une ch\u00e8vre, comme victime expiatoire. Et le sacrificateur fera pour lui l\u2019expiation de son p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.7","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:7","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>S\u2019il n\u2019a pas de quoi se procurer une brebis ou une ch\u00e8vre, il offrira en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel pour son p\u00e9ch\u00e9 deux tourterelles ou deux jeunes pigeons, l\u2019un comme victime expiatoire, l\u2019autre comme holocauste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.8","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:8","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il les apportera au sacrificateur, qui sacrifiera d\u2019abord celui qui doit servir de victime expiatoire. Le sacrificateur lui ouvrira la t\u00eate avec l\u2019ongle pr\u00e8s de la nuque, sans la s\u00e9parer;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.9","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:9","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>il fera sur un c\u00f4t\u00e9 de l\u2019autel l\u2019aspersion du sang de la victime expiatoire, et le reste du sang sera exprim\u00e9 au pied de l\u2019autel: c\u2019est un sacrifice d\u2019expiation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.10","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:10","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Il fera de l\u2019autre oiseau un holocauste, d\u2019apr\u00e8s les r\u00e8gles \u00e9tablies. C\u2019est ainsi que le sacrificateur fera pour cet homme l\u2019expiation du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.11","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:11","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>S\u2019il n\u2019a pas de quoi se procurer deux tourterelles ou deux jeunes pigeons, il apportera en offrande pour son p\u00e9ch\u00e9 un dixi\u00e8me d\u2019\u00e9pha de fleur de farine, comme offrande d\u2019expiation; il ne mettra point d\u2019huile dessus, et il n\u2019y ajoutera point d\u2019encens, car c\u2019est une offrande d\u2019expiation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.12","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:12","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il l\u2019apportera au sacrificateur, et le sacrificateur en prendra une poign\u00e9e comme souvenir, et il la br\u00fblera sur l\u2019autel, comme les offrandes consum\u00e9es par le feu devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel: c\u2019est une offrande d\u2019expiation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.13","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:13","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>C\u2019est ainsi que le sacrificateur fera pour cet homme l\u2019expiation du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commis \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de l\u2019une de ces choses, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9. Ce qui restera de l\u2019offrande sera pour le sacrificateur, comme dans l\u2019offrande en don.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.14","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:14","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les sacrifices de culpabilit\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-26: cf. No 5:5-8. Ps 19:13. \u00c9z 33:14-16. (1 Jn 2:1, 2.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.15","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:15","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Lorsque quelqu\u2019un commettra une infid\u00e9lit\u00e9 et p\u00e9chera involontairement \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard des choses consacr\u00e9es \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, il offrira en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel pour son p\u00e9ch\u00e9 un b\u00e9lier sans d\u00e9faut, pris du troupeau d\u2019apr\u00e8s ton estimation en sicles d\u2019argent, selon le sicle du sanctuaire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.16","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:16","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il donnera, en y ajoutant un cinqui\u00e8me, la valeur de la chose dont il a frustr\u00e9 le sanctuaire, et il la remettra au sacrificateur. Et le sacrificateur fera pour lui l\u2019expiation avec le b\u00e9lier offert en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.17","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:17","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Lorsque quelqu\u2019un p\u00e9chera en faisant, sans le savoir, contre l\u2019un des commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, des choses qui ne doivent point se faire, il se rendra coupable et sera charg\u00e9 de sa faute.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.18","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:18","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Il pr\u00e9sentera au sacrificateur en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9 un b\u00e9lier sans d\u00e9faut, pris du troupeau d\u2019apr\u00e8s ton estimation. Et le sacrificateur fera pour lui l\u2019expiation de la faute qu\u2019il a commise sans le savoir, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.19","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:19","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>C\u2019est un sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9. Cet homme s\u2019\u00e9tait rendu coupable envers l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.20","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:20","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.21","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:21","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Lorsque quelqu\u2019un p\u00e9chera et commettra une infid\u00e9lit\u00e9 envers l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en mentant \u00e0 son prochain au sujet d\u2019un d\u00e9p\u00f4t, d\u2019un objet confi\u00e9 \u00e0 sa garde, d\u2019une chose vol\u00e9e ou soustraite par fraude,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.22","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:22","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>en niant d\u2019avoir trouv\u00e9 une chose perdue, ou en faisant un faux serment sur une chose quelconque de nature \u00e0 constituer un p\u00e9ch\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.23","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:23","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>lorsqu\u2019il p\u00e9chera ainsi et se rendra coupable, il restituera la chose qu\u2019il a vol\u00e9e ou soustraite par fraude, la chose qui lui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 confi\u00e9e en d\u00e9p\u00f4t, la chose perdue qu\u2019il a trouv\u00e9e,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.24","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:24","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>ou la chose quelconque sur laquelle il a fait un faux serment. Il la restituera en son entier, y ajoutera un cinqui\u00e8me, et la remettra \u00e0 son propri\u00e9taire, le jour m\u00eame o\u00f9 il offrira son sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.25","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:25","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.005.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Il pr\u00e9sentera au sacrificateur en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel pour son p\u00e9ch\u00e9 un b\u00e9lier sans d\u00e9faut, pris du troupeau d\u2019apr\u00e8s ton estimation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.26","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.26","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 5:26","prev_osis_id":"Lev.005.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.006.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.5.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Et le sacrificateur fera pour lui l\u2019expiation devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il lui sera pardonn\u00e9, quelle que soit la faute dont il se sera rendu coupable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.6.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.6.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.5.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 5:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.5.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81f18ad0de4.00630216');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81f18ad0de4.00630216\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81f18ad0de4.00630216","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81f18ad0de4.00630216'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81f18ad0de4.00630216\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}